# init(_:)

**Initializer**

Creates an overlapping priority from the value.

## Declaration

```swift
init(_ rawValue: Float)
```

## Parameters

- **rawValue**: A value between [doc://com.apple.mapkit/documentation/MapKit/MKAnnotationViewZPriority/min] and [doc://com.apple.mapkit/documentation/MapKit/MKAnnotationViewZPriority/max].

## Initializers

- **init(rawValue:)**: Creates an overlapping priority from the value.
